title: Fort White routs Eastside, one win from district title
text:
Fort White routs Eastside, one win from district title 
Sat, Oct 24, 2015 @ 12:24 am 
The Times-Union 
FORT WHITE 42 
G’VILLE EASTSIDE 17 
Jacquez Pelham scored two touchdowns in the Indians’ convincing victory over Eastside (1-7). ... Don Robinson opened the scoring with a 39-yard touchdown rush for Fort White (6-2). ... The Indians can wrap up District 6-1A next week with a win over Hawthorne.
